    {
      "title": "New Treatment Approach for Liver Cirrhosis",
      "link": "https://dst.gov.in/new-approach-treatment-liver-cirrhosis",
      "author": null,
      "thumbnail": null,
      "summary": "- *Scientists* developed a novel method using *VEGF-C nanocarriers* to enhance lymphatic drainage in the liver and intestines affected by cirrhosis.\n- The approach aims to *reduce ascites* and *improve immune and lymphatic functions*, addressing complications in *decompensated cirrhosis*.\n- This research offers a promising *targeted therapy* that could lead to new treatments after further *clinical trials* in larger animals and humans.",
      "keywords": [
        "liver cirrhosis",
        "lymphatic system",
        "VEGF-C",
        "nanocarriers",
        "hepatology",
        "innovative therapy"
      ],
      "scores": {
        "scale": 7,
        "impact": 8,
        "novelty": 9,
        "longTermSignificance": 8
      },
      "pubDate": "2025-08-02T03:23:56.835Z"
    },
    {
      "title": "Himalayan clouds carry toxic metals, posing health risks",
      "link": "https://dst.gov.in/himalayan-clouds-carrying-toxic-metals-pose-health-risks",
      "author": null,
      "thumbnail": null,
      "summary": "*Clouds in the Himalayas are transporting toxic heavy metals like Cd, Cu, and Zn from polluted lowlands.*\n- These metals pose serious *health risks*, including carcinogenic and developmental diseases, especially through inhalation and contact.\n- The study highlights that *children* are 30% more vulnerable, with higher pollution levels over the Eastern Himalayas, mainly due to industrial emissions and traffic.*\n\n\"Heavy metal contamination in mountain clouds challenges the myth of *'clean'* mountain rain,\" emphasizing the need for further research on *atmospheric pollution* and public health impacts.",
      "keywords": [
        "Environmental Pollution",
        "Toxic Metals",
        "Himalayas",
        "Public Health",
        "Airborne Contaminants"
      ],
      "scores": {
        "scale": 8,
        "impact": 8,
        "novelty": 9,
        "longTermSignificance": 8
      },
      "pubDate": "2025-08-02T03:23:56.835Z"
    },
